  size overflow to mobile phones
- fixed bug in scan_and_attack and scan_and_info
- fixed bug in get_device_info
- vendor detection via ieee oui file (thanks to hosh - evilgenius.de
  for that great idea :)
- New menu design (thanks to ^_^)
- Updated bss to version 0.8

